ng-s%C4%A9/Sinh-t%E1%BB%AD-nh%C3%A0n-nhi-d%C4%A9/poem-NLrtL8QCgNQgkrUCWjvPEA">Sinh tử nhàn nhi dĩ - 生死閑而已</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-B%C3%ACnh/Tam-Nguy%C3%AAn-l%C3%BD/poem-1R8a4Q0W7od95IQ6iuXhaA">Tam Nguyên lý - 三元里</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-B%C3%ACnh/author-TIvot9ygcd7c2YjVBohAJw">Trương Duy Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/Th%C3%B9-Chu-gi%C3%A1m-k%E1%BB%B7-T%E1%BB%A9-Ph%E1%BB%A5/poem-3OQubNxaQmrMbk6IMp4qcA">Thù Chu giám kỷ Tứ Phụ - 酬朱監紀四輔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/author-py5Vb_484Rgr_jQ_nkfQjw">Cố Viêm Vũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Tr%E1%BB%87-kh%C3%A1ch/poem-PyWzZnf0hMDFGiRnoNoH4g">Trệ khách - 滯客</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
